snippet.title: Goose Goose Duck Story Cinematic
snippet.description:
Win10 and macOS

FREE TO PLAY Early Access April 29th, 2021:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1568590/Goose_Goose_Duck/

Join our discord to be a part of our growing community!
Discord: https://discord.gg/zfmTxYH82w

Our brand new social deception game is about to launch. Bring up to 16 friends together in this voice chat integrated game of deception, lies, and outright murder. Tons of new roles, cool game modes, and bajillion cosmetic options to unlock.
